<module>
    <h>sgìth</h>
    <p><g>sgìth</g>
        <en>tired</en> is a <a href="?xx=adjectives/simple_adjectives">simple adjective</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>dependents</h>
        <section>
            <h>specifier</h>
            <p>
                <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha mi <m>glé sgìth</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>I am very tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-predicate">
            <h>predicate</h>
            <p><g>sgìth</g> can be used as the predicate of the verb <a href="?gd=bi"
                ><g>bi</g></a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with a human subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri <m>sgìth</m>. Tha i <m>sgìth</m> ag obair anns an achadh.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is tired. She is tired working in the field.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha sibh trang ag obair anns an achadh agus tha sibh <m>sgìth</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>You are busy working in the field and you are tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri bheag <m>sgìth</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Little Mary is tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha mi fuar agus tha mi <m>sgìth</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>I am cold and I am tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil thu sgìth?</gd>
                        <tr>Are you tired?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 11</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Nach eil thu sgìth?</gd>
                        <tr>Aren’t you tired?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

</module>
